{
  "stem": "11296.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They brought it in-- nobody asked your size, they just handed it over to you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I don't really remember-- I remember I got a dress, and I remember I got a coat.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "My head was nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They gave us a piece of cloth to put on the head.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "The shoes, they didn't match to my feet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So I'm staying and looking at my sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "She looks at me, and I looked-- and nobody could recognize themself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I said, my gosh.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I see all the things staying there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Nobody touched them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The clothes, when we took them-- it was in another room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I picked myself up, and I jumped in the other room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Really, I didn't think, you know, they could kill me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I grabbed my shoes, my boots-- I was still standing there-- I grabbed my boots.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was afraid they're going to see I have a beautiful black, leather boots.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I took the knife-- I found a knife there-- and I cut down the upper part from the boots, and I put on just the bottoms.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had my shoes-- It was from the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so after a few hours, this took, you know, they had to tattoo us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was going after A, B, C-- so my name is under the K, so it took a long time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when everybody was tattooed, they divided us, a part of us, a hundred they took to another place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Really not to Birkenau, to a satellite from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And me and my sister and all the other people, they tooked us out from the bath, and they tooked us to our barrack.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The barrack's number was number eight.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
